return_method_desc: Traced by member of the public
circumstances: Leon Hancock, who had recently withdrawn from university, was last seen with his uncle, Leigh Hancock, at the fairground near 1 Pitfour Street, Dundee, before heading towards an alleyway off 71 Lothian Crescent. His absence raised concern until he was found by a member of the public.
